  "title": "it security pre-sales / solutions manager",
  "description": "<p>About the role</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Lead and Mentor a Team: Manage and coach a team of pre-sales engineers, providing technical guidance, career development, and performance feedback.</li>\n  <li>Technical Expertise: Act as a subject matter expert for a wide range of cybersecurity solutions.</li>\n  <li>Customer Engagement: Work directly with the sales team and customers to understand their business challenges and technical requirements, then design and present tailored solutions that address their needs.</li>\n  <li>Solution Demonstrations: Develop and deliver engaging product demonstrations, technical presentations, and proofs-of-concept (POCs)</li>\n  <li>Public Speaking: Actively participate in and host webinars, workshops, and other industry events as a speaker or panelist.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Skills and experience required</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum of 6 years of hands-on cybersecurity pre-sales experience.</li>\n  <li>Proven experience leading a pre-sales or technical team.</li>\n  <li>Extensive knowledge across a wide range of cybersecurity domains</li>\n  <li>Strong communication and presentation skills<br>\n<br>\n<br>\nTo apply online please use the apply function, alternatively you may contact Chloe Chen at chloe.chen(@)randstad.com.sg. (EA: 94C3609 /R1768253)</li>\n</ul>",
